data.description: Price reduced to sell. Very nice home sits on fully fenced five acres 2 miles outside of Strasburg. Lots of finished square footage. Five bedrooms and additional office space, three full bathrooms. Basement is 90% finished. 9' ceilings both up and down. Large oversized three car attached garage and additional 24x40 Cleary shop with concrete flooring. Large wind break with nice trees along property line. Hardwood floors, 42 inch cabinets in kitchen, pantry, all appliances except W/D. Includes gas fireplace, ceiling fans, built in shelving and nice covered back patio. Exterior has sprinkler system, dog run, chicken coop and small shed. New roof and gutters.
